{
  "stem": "5470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ones they could pick up at that time, yes, and they took them as hostage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And not all of them have been-- been in a camp for a long time, but they were for some time anyhow arrested and to stay there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, really, they didn't do very much in that particular time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So after six weeks, I came back again and into the open, showed myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that was the first reaction already shortly in the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In July-- that was in July '40, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now my life started, so far as possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that was in food distribution is where I started off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of my connections, when they started off by transporting Jewish people out of the country, that's where I was contacted if I could do something about it too or if I was willing to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went over to Westerbork in July '42 and came in contact with the camp commander-- the death camp commander-- that was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were looking for an employment for me to get me into the camp so I could do what I wanted to and see if he could sabotage everything what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he appointed me to his aid, the camp commander, just as his aid, so that they could get the full picture of what was going on, if I was employed in a, say, a normal position, you had hardly any contact, and you didn't know what was going on there at all.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But because of that appointment, being his aid, I got to know everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was going on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the letters which were written by the Germans and what their intentions were.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
